(9, 4, '', 'Start a Payments site like PayPal with this powerful turn-key Payment processor script', 'What can you do with this incredible Payment processor script ? - Be a universal payment processor : Your users can sign up to create a BUY NOW button – and using it collect payments from a variety Payment gateways like PayPal, Stripe, Payza, Bitcoins, 2Checkout, Authorize.Net, SagePay, Pin Payments etc. - Run a subscription billing site like RECURLY.COM : Your users can generate a Subscription payment link – and using it start collecting subscription payments from anywhere on the web. - Run a site like GUMROAD.COM : This script has features for you to run a digital download store as well. People can upload a product – create a BUY NOW button and promote it anywhere ! What do you get in this deal ? A powerful Payment processor script : worth $5000 Comes with a powerful admin panel to control the site end-to-end : worth $1000 $8000 worth FREE goodies from our Sponsors', '. Rating: 0.0/5 (0 votes) Please login to vote.', 'ID #1667 ', ' Wednesday, 11 June, 2014  02:08 ', ' Hits: 217'),
